[[File:Cook (Lumbridge) chathead.png|left]]
The '''cook''' is [[Duke Horacio]]'s personal cook. He usually seems unprepared, but with the player's help, he prepares great food. He is the starting point for the [[Cook's Assistant]] and [[Recipe for Disaster]] [[quests]]. He can be found in the [[Lumbridge Castle]] kitchen on the {{FloorNumber|uk=0}}. The cook has 4 children and a goat.

When the Cook's Assistant quest is completed, the player is granted use of his [[Cooking range (Lumbridge Castle)|magical range]], which has a lower chance of burning [[food]] compared to other [[range]]s.
{{clear|left}}

==Treasure Trails==
* {{Anagram|The cook|medium|OK CO}}. He will present the player with a challenge scroll which asks, ''"How many cannons does Lumbridge Castle have?"'', the answer to which is 9. <br/>
* {{CrypticNPC|The cook|beginner|In the place Duke Horacio calls home, talk to a man with a hat dropped by goblins.}}

